{"tid":1795778,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方去信廣播處長指港台報道「誤導」聽眾","createTime":"2019-12-24T07:16:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T09:05:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9097a4bba75ef0791dfcc223b5f919a7d8eefc1e","tid":1795778,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20191224_20191224-145716.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20191224_20191224-145716.jpg&h=0a0f53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科總警司郭嘉銓去信廣播處處長梁家榮，指香港電台昨日晨早新聞時段中，有關星期日中環愛丁堡廣場舉行集會報道，所用的字眼與事實不符，會誤導聽眾，認為報道會加深大眾對警隊的誤會。<br />\n<br />\n警方在信中指，愛丁堡廣場舉行集會期間，有人違法拆下旗桿上的國旗並擲在地上，警方才上前拾起國旗以免遭受破壞，但有人襲擊警察，投擲水樽等物件，並企圖搶奪因在現場襲警而被捕的一名男子，現場一遍混亂，警察才需要使用所需最低武力控制場面，但港台在報道中指在場人士掟水樽等物品「還擊」，令聽眾誤會是警方主動使用武力。"},{"pid":"3dc617e8619b3ccffd0bc9761d04a6295c0c5145","tid":1795778,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:17:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1243031&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1243031%26csid%3D261_341&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpgDpGYGFnKQRHckm7FIFNPY%3D&h=c036fe72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1243031&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"20bd5221445158969f165502cfb488f8c738bf34","tid":1795778,"uid":131691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:19:19.000Z","msg":"襲擊警甴係香港人嘅公民責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"101a116162d2b295f1cb12912339a038398cc085","tid":1795778,"uid":30647,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"&quot;所用的字眼與事實不符&quot;<br />\n警謊記者會呢? er er er 呢?"},{"pid":"5575368097139484b9278fe1f92